{
  "stem": "3212.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "When we wanted to turn, we have to talk together that we'll turn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "All-- all-- the whole bed-- all together, we had to turn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "People urinated from the other floor, from the second bunk or the third.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "We had-- we were laying on the beds on wood, nothing underneath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "At night, people came in and stole this piece of metal, or killed people to get this piece of metal for the next day's soup.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Then they put us in Block 66, where we were all children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Block 66 in Buchenwald was block-- children's block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Again, we have to-- had to start working.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We-- we start working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They took us out of the camp to mountains, where we had to load rocks on a-- was a little railing with--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wagons, little wagons that we had to put stones in it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I remember during the march, when we all marched in Buchenwald to work, we had to sing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when-- we had to sing a song that goes something like this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SINGING IN GERMAN]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we had to-- when we marched, we had to sing it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the camp, the kapo that was in our block.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Before we had to march, he teached us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you have to-- when you march, you have to sing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The song was like, the-- the heaven is red, and the-- and the-- the forest is black.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SINGING SOFTLY] And-- and-- [SINGING SOFTLY] And we are carrying our baggage in the back, a little bit bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In our heart, we have-- we are worried about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we know how beautiful the-- it is in the freedom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Buchenwald, we don't cry, and we don't scream, because we know that one day will come, and we will be free.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
